<h3>Service <code>hangouts.send_message</code></h3>
<p>Sends a message to the given conversations.</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Service data attribute</th>
<th>Optional</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>target</td>
<td>List of targets with id or name. [Required]</td>
<td>[{“id”: “UgxrXzVrARmjx_C6AZx4AaABAagBo-6UCw”}, {“name”: “Test Conversation”}]</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>message</td>
<td>List of message segments, only the “text” field is required in every segment. [Required]</td>
<td>[{“text”:“test”, “is_bold”: false, “is_italic”: false, “is_strikethrough”: false, “is_underline”: false, “parse_str”: false, “link_target”: “http://google.com”}, …]</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>data</td>
<td>Extra options</td>
<td>{“image_file”: “path”} / {“image_url”: “url”}</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
